    "name": "Baetriov",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Baetriovs are unique occult vampires who use ancient vile rituals to store their life force in a pool of blood, which must be periodically refreshed by human sacrifice. So long as their blood wells remain fresh and intact, baetriovs can remain forever young and handsome, gathering cults of personality to provide new victims."
        }
    ],
